Class RankEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • acp.beans.RankEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class RankEntry
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    RankEntry is the base data structure used by the ranking algorithm. Each source document is represented by one object.

    Ng Chin Hui
